PEPPERONI: PORK, BEEF, SALT, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF LACTIC ACID STARTER CULTURE, OLEORESIN OF PAPRIKA, SODIUM NITRITE, BHA, BHT, CITRIC ACID. MAY ALSO CONTAIN 2% OR LESS OF SPICES, SPICE EXTRACTIVES, DEXTROSE, SUGAR, FLAVORINGS, SODIUM ASCORBATE, WATER, GARLIC POWDER.
